# India Telecom Expense Management Market Size & Outlook, 2030
The telecom expense management market in India is expected to reach a projected revenue of US$ 545.0 million by 2030, with a compound annual growth rate of 14.8% from 2023 to 2030.

## Overview
* Revenue in 2022: US$ 180.8 million
* Forecast in 2030: US$ 545.0 million
* CAGR from 2023 to 2030: 14.8%

## Market Segmentation
The India telecom expense management market is segmented into:
* Component: Solution, Service
* Solution: Sourcing Management, Ordering and Provisioning Management, Usage Management, Dispute Management, Invoice Management
* Service: Managed Services, Hosted Services
* Deployment: On-premise, Cloud
* Enterprise: Large Sized Enterprises, Small and Medium Sized Enterprises (SMEs)
* Industry Vertical: Healthcare, BFSI, Consumer Goods & Retail, IT and Telecom, Manufacturing & Automotive
* Regions: Latin America, Europe, North America, Middle East & Africa, Asia Pacific
* Countries: U.S., Canada, UK, Germany, France, Italy, Netherlands, China, India, Japan, Australia, South Korea, Brazil, Mexico, Chile, Argentina, UAE, Saudi Arabia, South Africa

