## Market Highlights
* The India telecom expense management market generated a revenue of USD 180.8 million in 2022 and is expected to reach USD 545.0 million by 2030.
* The India market is expected to grow at a CAGR of 14.8% from 2023 to 2030.
* Solution was the largest revenue-generating component in 2022.
* Service is the most lucrative component segment, registering the fastest growth during the forecast period.

